full_product_description:
Revolutionize your hairstyling routine with the InStyler Ionic Pro 4-in-1 Hair Straightener, Curling Iron, Hot Brush, and Flat Iron. This versatile tool combines four styling functions in one, allowing you to achieve smooth, sleek straight hair or voluminous curls effortlessly. The advanced Dual Ionic Ceramic Technology helps reduce frizz while adding shine and body, ensuring your hair stays healthy and burn-free during styling.

With multiple heat settings up to 400°F, the InStyler Ionic Pro is designed to work on all hair types, from fine to coarse, giving you full control over your styling preferences. Its cool touch ionic bristles allow for tangle-free, safe styling, while the non-slip rubber grip and 360-degree swivel cord provide comfort and ease of use. Whether you want to create straight, smooth hair or bouncy curls, this all-in-one tool will meet your every need.

Plus, its automatic safety shut-off feature gives you peace of mind, ensuring the device turns off after use. Compact and portable, the InStyler Ionic Pro is ideal for travel, allowing you to maintain your style wherever you go.

full_product_description:
The Tulip auto curler's innovative automatic curling technology lets you achieve perfect curls and waves every time without tangling or damaging hair. Curling your hair has never been so fast and easy with the simple tap of a button, you can have beachy waves in just 3 seconds, soft curls in 8 seconds and striking tight curls in 12 seconds. With the unique open barrel design of the Tulip, your hair is visible and exposed at all times, preventing hair from getting tangled and becoming jammed in the unit. The open design and ample space surrounding the barrel also makes it easy for the Tulip to curl long and thick hair. The lightweight ergonomic design of the Tulip makes curling your hair easy and comfortable. Throughout the entire styling process, the Tulip is held in a natural vertical position with a relaxed grip, putting no strain or stress on your hand or wrist.





Open ceramic barrel designed with anti-tangle technology





2-way rotation with 3 rotation settings to curl left, curl right or alternate





3 heat settings range from 350 to 430 degrees Fahrenheit to accommodate all hair types





3 timer settings to achieve a variety of looks from beachy waves to tight striking curls





Safety guard for burn-free styling

full_product_description: The 2 in 1 Multi - Functional Hairbrush is a revolutionary styling tool that combines the capabilities of straightening and curling into one convenient device. Say goodbye to the hassle of juggling multiple hair styling tools, as this innovative product streamlines your haircare routine.​ Designed with precision, the hairbrush features a unique barrel and bristle configuration. The bristles are carefully engineered to glide smoothly through your hair, detangling it gently while the heating elements work their magic. The instyler Dual Purpose Automatic Straightening or Curling Magic mechanism is truly a game - changer. With a simple flick of the wrist, you can transform your hair from straight to wavy or vice versa.​ This professional - grade hot brush styling flat iron hairdressing tool comes equipped with an adjustable heater. Whether you have fine, delicate hair or thick, coarse locks, you can customize the temperature to suit your hair type. The temperature range typically spans from a gentle heat suitable for sensitive hair to a higher heat setting for those with more stubborn curls or waves. This ensures that you can achieve the perfect style without causing damage to your precious tresses.​ The device heats up rapidly, saving you valuable time in the morning rush. It also has a built - in safety feature, such as an automatic shut - off after a certain period of inactivity, giving you peace of mind while using it. The ergonomic handle provides a comfortable grip, allowing for easy maneuverability around your head, ensuring that you can reach every strand with ease.
